### Workflow 1.1 — View Ad Server Analytics Dashboard

**Entry:** Left Nav → Product Ads → Analytics → Ad Server Analytics

Step 1 → Page loads at `/productAds/anaytics/adServerAnalytics`
Step 2 → System displays 6 KPI cards in a row: Requests, Response(%), Program CPC, Program CPM, CTR, Ad Impressions
Step 3 → System displays two Daily Performance Trend charts side by side
Step 4 → System displays Page Level Contribution chart below the trend charts
Step 5 → System displays Daily Page Performance Report section with Chart/List toggle
Step 6 → System displays Available Advertising SKU By Hour table at the bottom
Step 7 → Default date range is applied (Last 7 Days)
Step 8 → Default page filter is "All Pages"
Step 9 → All charts and KPI cards render with current data
Step 10 → User can see all performance metrics at a glance
✅ Workflow Complete — Dashboard is fully loaded and ready for interaction

---

### Workflow 1.2 — Filter by Page Type

**Entry:** Ad Server Analytics Dashboard (loaded)

Step 1 → User locates "All Pages" global filter dropdown at top of page
Step 2 → User clicks dropdown to expand options
Step 3 → System displays: All Pages, Home, Category, Search, Product, PSP, Custom, Purchase, TPA
Step 4 → User selects desired page type (e.g., "Category")
Step 5 → System closes dropdown and shows selected filter label
Step 6 → All 6 KPI cards update with filtered data
Step 7 → Both Daily Performance Trend charts update
Step 8 → Page Level Contribution chart updates
Step 9 → Daily Page Performance Report updates (both Chart and List views)
Step 10 → Available Advertising SKU By Hour table updates
Step 11 → Filter label shows selected page type
✅ Workflow Complete — All data is filtered to the selected page type

---

