## Notes & Observations

1. **URL Typo:** All Analytics URLs use `/anaytics/` (missing the second `a`) instead of `/analytics/`. This is a known routing issue in the platform.

2. **PRO Features:** Demand & Supply and Live Analytics are gated behind a PRO subscription badge.

3. **CPC vs CPM Symmetry:** Yield Controls CPC and CPM pages are structurally identical — every feature in CPC has a direct CPM equivalent with the same workflows.

4. **Keyword Bid Setting Symmetry:** Same pattern — CPC and CPM pages are mirrors of each other.

5. **Campaign Bulk Actions Upload Pattern:** All 5 Campaign Bulk Action pages follow the same pattern: Download template → Edit in Excel → Upload .xlsx. The key differentiator is what the template contains (blank vs pre-filled, all campaigns vs ACTIVE/PAUSED only).

6. **Review & Apply Pattern:** All changes in Yield Controls (CPC/CPM) require a 2-step confirmation: make changes → click Review & Apply → review modal → click Apply. Changes are NOT auto-saved.

7. **Activity Log:** Only available on Yield Controls (CPC and CPM) pages. Not present on Analytics or Campaign Bulk Action pages.

8. **Inline Editing:** Only available on Yield Controls (CPC and CPM) tables. All other sections are read-only or bulk-upload based.

9. **Column Picker:** Available on Ad Server Analytics (List View), Demand & Supply (both views), Live Analytics (Advertiser & Campaign Reports), and Yield Controls (CPC/CPM).

10. **No Date Picker on Live Analytics:** Unlike other Analytics pages, Live Analytics shows real-time data only and has no date range filter.

11. **Product Selection Limit:** 100,000 products per upload — significantly larger than the 1,000 campaign limit for Create Campaign.

12. **Download Variants:** Some pages offer only a blank template ("Download"), while others offer a pre-populated file ("Download file for all advertisers"). Create Campaign and Product Selection use blank templates; Update/Activate/Pause Campaigns and Keyword Bid Settings use pre-populated files.

